sqlQuery: SELECT item.i_color, item.i_units, web_page.wp_web_page_id, MIN(web_sales.ws_ext_ship_cost) as agg_0, MIN(web_sales.ws_web_page_sk + web_page.wp_char_count) as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM web_page JOIN web_sales ON web_page.wp_web_page_sk = web_sales.ws_web_page_sk JOIN item ON web_sales.ws_item_sk = item.i_item_sk  WHERE item.i_manufact_id >= 160.0663267518406 AND web_page.wp_autogen_flag IN ('Y', 'N') AND (web_page.wp_web_page_id = 'AAAAAAAANJAAAAAA' OR (web_page.wp_type = 'feedback' AND web_page.wp_web_page_id = 'AAAAAAAAMFAAAAAA')) AND web_sales.ws_quantity <= 59.57187766462889 AND (web_page.wp_autogen_flag IN ('Y', 'N') OR (web_page.wp_autogen_flag IN ('Y') AND web_page.wp_autogen_flag IS NOT NULL)) AND item.i_manufact NOT LIKE '%stn%' AND item.i_current_price <= 3.7182270825488595 AND item.i_rec_end_date NOT LIKE '%2000-10-26%' AND item.i_color = 'indian' AND web_page.wp_url = 'http://www.foo.com' GROUP BY item.i_color, item.i_units, web_page.wp_web_page_id ORDER BY item.i_color, item.i_units, web_page.wp_web_page_id;

SELECT MAX(store_returns.sr_reason_sk) as agg_0 FROM store_returns JOIN date_dim ON store_returns.sr_returned_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN web_page ON date_dim.d_date_sk = web_page.wp_access_date_sk  WHERE date_dim.d_date_sk <= 2456435.3437731005 AND web_page.wp_web_page_id NOT LIKE '%AAAAAAAAAKAAAAAA%' AND date_dim.d_weekend = 'Y' AND date_dim.d_current_week != 'N' AND store_returns.sr_return_amt <= 99.64725794190679 AND (web_page.wp_access_date_sk >= 2452632.3342475104 OR (web_page.wp_web_page_sk <= 149.7549722279922 AND web_page.wp_access_date_sk <= 2452592.853372082)) AND store_returns.sr_return_ship_cost <= 880.4281516790094 AND (date_dim.d_year <= 1929.4345651260712 OR (date_dim.d_following_holiday IN ('Y', 'N') AND date_dim.d_year >= 1903.1237965889738)) AND (web_page.wp_rec_start_date IN ('1999-09-04') OR (web_page.wp_rec_start_date IN ('2000-09-03', '1999-09-04', '1997-09-03', '2001-09-03') AND web_page.wp_rec_start_date LIKE '%1997-09-03%')) AND date_dim.d_same_day_ly <= 2424807.3073689654 AND (web_page.wp_autogen_flag = 'N' OR (web_page.wp_type LIKE '%ad%' AND web_page.wp_autogen_flag = 'Y')) AND web_page.wp_rec_start_date LIKE '%200%1-09-03%' AND web_page.wp_url NOT LIKE '%http://www.foo.com%' AND store_returns.sr_item_sk <= 49669.28877265654 AND (date_dim.d_qoy <= 3.0 OR (date_dim.d_qoy <= 2.7554928577973756 AND date_dim.d_qoy <= 2.0)) AND web_page.wp_char_count >= 1542.280091913042;

SELECT date_dim.d_quarter_name, date_dim.d_holiday, household_demographics.hd_buy_potential, SUM(date_dim.d_dow + date_dim.d_same_day_lq) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM reason JOIN catalog_returns ON reason.r_reason_sk = catalog_returns.cr_reason_sk JOIN date_dim ON catalog_returns.cr_returned_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN catalog_page ON date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_page.cp_start_date_sk JOIN household_demographics ON catalog_returns.cr_refunded_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk JOIN customer ON catalog_returns.cr_returning_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk  WHERE catalog_returns.cr_returned_date_sk >= 2452829.400297571 AND household_demographics.hd_buy_potential IN ('>10000', '0-500', '1001-5000') AND customer.c_last_name != 'Sipes' AND reason.r_reason_sk <= 30.484956651239717 AND customer.c_preferred_cust_flag IN ('Y') AND customer.c_first_sales_date_sk <= 2449305.295522215 AND customer.c_salutation IN ('Ms.') AND customer.c_birth_month >= 11.138553898495958 AND catalog_returns.cr_warehouse_sk <= 10.0 GROUP BY date_dim.d_quarter_name, date_dim.d_holiday, household_demographics.hd_buy_potential HAVING COUNT(*) >= 0 ORDER BY date_dim.d_quarter_name, date_dim.d_holiday, household_demographics.hd_buy_potential;

SELECT time_dim.t_shift, COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM time_dim JOIN catalog_sales ON time_dim.t_time_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_time_sk  WHERE catalog_sales.cs_ext_ship_cost <= 352.52349340469453 AND catalog_sales.cs_ext_wholesale_cost <= 2204.796471481882 AND catalog_sales.cs_net_paid_inc_tax >= 218.9209264764219 AND (time_dim.t_meal_time LIKE '%lunc%h%' OR time_dim.t_meal_time NOT LIKE '%lunch%' OR time_dim.t_meal_time NOT LIKE '%breakfast%') AND catalog_sales.cs_ship_customer_sk <= 421974.7344066446 GROUP BY time_dim.t_shift ORDER BY time_dim.t_shift;

SELECT customer.c_preferred_cust_flag, AVG(web_sales.ws_net_paid_inc_tax + web_sales.ws_quantity) as agg_0, SUM(customer.c_customer_sk + web_sales.ws_ext_tax) as agg_1, SUM(web_sales.ws_ext_sales_price + web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk) as agg_2 FROM time_dim JOIN web_sales ON time_dim.t_time_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_time_sk JOIN web_returns ON time_dim.t_time_sk = web_returns.wr_returned_time_sk JOIN customer ON web_sales.ws_bill_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk  WHERE customer.c_birth_country NOT LIKE '%UNITED%' AND web_returns.wr_returned_date_sk <= 2451746.0213097306 AND time_dim.t_sub_shift LIKE '%afternoon%' AND web_returns.wr_refunded_cdemo_sk >= 520944.9053502769 AND time_dim.t_meal_time != 'dinner' AND web_sales.ws_web_site_sk <= 9.577711310238222 AND customer.c_first_sales_date_sk >= 2449662.645547458 AND time_dim.t_shift NOT LIKE '%fir%st%' AND customer.c_birth_day >= 6.608844396755836 GROUP BY customer.c_preferred_cust_flag HAVING SUM(customer.c_customer_sk + web_sales.ws_ext_tax) >= 250103.6898447931 ORDER BY customer.c_preferred_cust_flag LIMIT 100;

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, MAX(date_dim.d_same_day_ly) as agg_1 FROM ship_mode JOIN catalog_returns ON ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk = catalog_returns.cr_ship_mode_sk JOIN customer ON catalog_returns.cr_returning_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk JOIN date_dim ON customer.c_first_shipto_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN time_dim ON catalog_returns.cr_returned_time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk JOIN web_sales ON customer.c_customer_sk = web_sales.ws_ship_customer_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON customer.c_customer_sk = catalog_sales.cs_ship_customer_sk JOIN household_demographics ON catalog_returns.cr_refunded_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk  WHERE customer.c_birth_year >= 1990.496711724422 AND (web_sales.ws_ext_tax <= 33.63932125324815 OR web_sales.ws_sold_time_sk >= 82487.00811296968 OR web_sales.ws_ext_tax >= 0.0) AND household_demographics.hd_demo_sk <= 6754.499773428319 AND web_sales.ws_ext_ship_cost >= 12.201890157320449 AND time_dim.t_shift IN ('third', 'first') AND time_dim.t_am_pm NOT LIKE '%A%M%' AND (customer.c_first_sales_date_sk >= 2450720.1588972216 OR customer.c_last_name != 'Rawls') AND time_dim.t_minute <= 53.60099089369679 AND catalog_sales.cs_ship_mode_sk >= 17.033822683271115 AND ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_id = 'AAAAAAAAABAAAAAA' LIMIT 100;

SELECT time_dim.t_sub_shift, MIN(web_sales.ws_sold_time_sk + catalog_sales.cs_net_profit) as agg_0, SUM(web_sales.ws_ext_ship_cost + store_returns.sr_cdemo_sk) as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM catalog_page JOIN date_dim ON catalog_page.cp_end_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN store_returns ON date_dim.d_date_sk = store_returns.sr_returned_date_sk JOIN promotion ON date_dim.d_date_sk = promotion.p_start_date_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_ship_date_sk JOIN catalog_returns ON date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_returns.cr_returned_date_sk JOIN ship_mode ON catalog_returns.cr_ship_mode_sk = ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk JOIN web_sales ON ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk = web_sales.ws_ship_mode_sk JOIN web_site ON web_sales.ws_web_site_sk = web_site.web_site_sk JOIN call_center ON catalog_sales.cs_call_center_sk = call_center.cc_call_center_sk JOIN time_dim ON catalog_returns.cr_returned_time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk  WHERE time_dim.t_am_pm NOT LIKE '%P%M%' AND web_site.web_tax_percentage >= 0.07 AND (call_center.cc_zip != '59231' OR (call_center.cc_mkt_desc LIKE '%are%as%' AND call_center.cc_zip NOT LIKE '%33604%')) AND catalog_page.cp_department = 'DEPARTMENT' AND time_dim.t_second <= 2.4663523759565424 AND date_dim.d_first_dom >= 2435236.085534791 AND store_returns.sr_reason_sk <= 9.89699496032371 AND ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk >= 19.73545649282033 AND date_dim.d_qoy >= 4.0 AND date_dim.d_current_day != 'N' AND (web_site.web_county = 'Williamson County' OR (web_site.web_county = 'Ziebach County' AND web_site.web_county LIKE '%Cou%nty%')) AND (store_returns.sr_return_time_sk <= 53732.698009138614 OR store_returns.sr_store_credit >= 161.49235531386415) GROUP BY time_dim.t_sub_shift ORDER BY time_dim.t_sub_shift;

SELECT store.s_company_name, date_dim.d_current_month, store.s_street_number, AVG(web_sales.ws_order_number + web_sales.ws_net_paid_inc_ship_tax) as agg_0 FROM store JOIN date_dim ON store.s_closed_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN web_sales ON date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_ship_date_sk JOIN customer_address ON web_sales.ws_ship_addr_sk = customer_address.ca_address_sk  WHERE customer_address.ca_state IN ('KY', 'ND', 'RI', 'MS', 'OH', 'IN', 'NC', 'NM', 'CO', 'GA') AND web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk <= 2451893.0359449396 AND (store.s_state NOT LIKE '%TN%' OR store.s_division_name NOT LIKE '%Unknown%') AND customer_address.ca_suite_number NOT LIKE '%380%' AND store.s_street_name = '2nd Oak' GROUP BY store.s_company_name, date_dim.d_current_month, store.s_street_number ORDER BY store.s_company_name, date_dim.d_current_month, store.s_street_number;

SELECT call_center.cc_street_name, web_site.web_site_id, AVG(web_sales.ws_web_page_sk + time_dim.t_hour) as agg_0, SUM(web_returns.wr_returning_cdemo_sk + web_page.wp_link_count) as agg_1, MIN(catalog_returns.cr_call_center_sk) as agg_2 FROM inventory JOIN date_dim ON inventory.inv_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN web_site ON date_dim.d_date_sk = web_site.web_open_date_sk JOIN web_sales ON web_site.web_site_sk = web_sales.ws_web_site_sk JOIN time_dim ON web_sales.ws_sold_time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk JOIN web_page ON date_dim.d_date_sk = web_page.wp_access_date_sk JOIN web_returns ON time_dim.t_time_sk = web_returns.wr_returned_time_sk JOIN call_center ON date_dim.d_date_sk = call_center.cc_closed_date_sk JOIN customer_demographics ON web_returns.wr_refunded_cdemo_sk = customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk JOIN catalog_returns ON customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk = catalog_returns.cr_refunded_cdemo_sk  WHERE web_sales.ws_warehouse_sk >= 1.0 AND catalog_returns.cr_ship_mode_sk >= 7.76963738666881 AND (web_page.wp_url LIKE '%http://www.foo.com%' OR web_page.wp_url != 'http://www.foo.com') AND customer_demographics.cd_marital_status IN ('M', 'W') AND date_dim.d_holiday != 'Y' GROUP BY call_center.cc_street_name, web_site.web_site_id ORDER BY call_center.cc_street_name, web_site.web_site_id LIMIT 10;

SELECT time_dim.t_shift, customer.c_salutation, date_dim.d_holiday, AVG(catalog_sales.cs_sold_time_sk + catalog_sales.cs_sales_price) as agg_0 FROM ship_mode JOIN catalog_sales ON ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk = catalog_sales.cs_ship_mode_sk JOIN customer ON catalog_sales.cs_ship_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk JOIN date_dim ON customer.c_first_sales_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN catalog_page ON date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_page.cp_start_date_sk JOIN customer_demographics ON catalog_sales.cs_ship_cdemo_sk = customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk JOIN time_dim ON catalog_sales.cs_sold_time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk  WHERE catalog_page.cp_department != 'DEPARTMENT' AND (customer_demographics.cd_gender != 'F' OR customer_demographics.cd_education_status = '2 yr Degree') AND date_dim.d_current_week != 'N' AND time_dim.t_hour >= 14.91111551378998 AND time_dim.t_minute <= 26.519428505111225 AND customer.c_birth_month >= 1.9830139242563745 AND time_dim.t_sub_shift IN ('evening') AND (catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk <= 2451083.750204252 OR (catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk <= 2451282.4972198177 AND catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk <= 2451813.8297057333)) AND customer.c_birth_country IN ('NAURU', 'RWANDA', 'NIGERIA', 'NIUE', 'ICELAND', 'MONGOLIA', 'GABON') AND ship_mode.sm_type IN ('TWO DAY', 'OVERNIGHT', 'EXPRESS', 'NEXT DAY', 'LIBRARY', 'REGULAR') AND date_dim.d_current_year IN ('N', 'Y') AND customer_demographics.cd_credit_rating LIKE '%Risk%' AND date_dim.d_weekend = 'N' AND customer.c_first_name != 'Corrinne' GROUP BY time_dim.t_shift, customer.c_salutation, date_dim.d_holiday ORDER BY time_dim.t_shift, customer.c_salutation, date_dim.d_holiday;

SELECT MAX(catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk + date_dim.d_last_dom) as agg_0 FROM customer JOIN catalog_returns ON customer.c_customer_sk = catalog_returns.cr_returning_customer_sk JOIN customer_address ON catalog_returns.cr_returning_addr_sk = customer_address.ca_address_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON customer_address.ca_address_sk = catalog_sales.cs_ship_addr_sk JOIN date_dim ON catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN customer_demographics ON catalog_sales.cs_ship_cdemo_sk = customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk  WHERE catalog_sales.cs_bill_cdemo_sk >= 62938.023202260745 AND catalog_returns.cr_ship_mode_sk >= 9.415494158238683 AND customer_demographics.cd_purchase_estimate >= 5452.860839969926 AND customer.c_salutation IS NOT NULL AND customer.c_birth_country = 'GUINEA';

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM web_returns JOIN customer ON web_returns.wr_refunded_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk JOIN web_sales ON customer.c_customer_sk = web_sales.ws_ship_customer_sk JOIN customer_address ON web_returns.wr_returning_addr_sk = customer_address.ca_address_sk JOIN date_dim ON customer.c_first_shipto_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk  WHERE web_returns.wr_item_sk >= 22439.227679610573 AND customer.c_preferred_cust_flag IN ('Y') AND date_dim.d_weekend IN ('Y') AND date_dim.d_current_month = 'N' AND customer_address.ca_city NOT LIKE '%O%ak%' AND customer.c_last_name != 'Brewer' AND customer_address.ca_address_sk >= 56171.648000202105 AND customer_address.ca_country = 'United States' AND date_dim.d_current_day != 'N' AND web_sales.ws_ship_hdemo_sk <= 5522.954415645372;

SELECT date_dim.d_day_name, MAX(date_dim.d_fy_quarter_seq + catalog_sales.cs_quantity) as agg_0, MAX(catalog_page.cp_catalog_page_sk + catalog_sales.cs_ext_discount_amt) as agg_1, MIN(catalog_sales.cs_sold_time_sk + catalog_sales.cs_list_price) as agg_2 FROM catalog_page JOIN catalog_sales ON catalog_page.cp_catalog_page_sk = catalog_sales.cs_catalog_page_sk JOIN date_dim ON catalog_page.cp_start_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN customer_demographics ON catalog_sales.cs_ship_cdemo_sk = customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk JOIN ship_mode ON catalog_sales.cs_ship_mode_sk = ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk  WHERE customer_demographics.cd_credit_rating IN ('High Risk', 'Good', 'Low Risk', 'Unknown') AND customer_demographics.cd_marital_status = 'W' AND ship_mode.sm_contract != '2mM8l' AND catalog_page.cp_catalog_number <= 66.53304277113867 AND (catalog_page.cp_description NOT LIKE '%politic%al%' OR catalog_page.cp_type NOT LIKE '%bi-annual%') AND (date_dim.d_holiday != 'Y' OR date_dim.d_holiday = 'N') AND date_dim.d_quarter_name = '2081Q2' AND catalog_page.cp_catalog_page_number >= 35.006640719034266 AND catalog_page.cp_department NOT LIKE '%DEP%ARTMENT%' AND ship_mode.sm_type LIKE '%REGUL%AR%' AND ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk <= 14.446333069898694 AND date_dim.d_qoy >= 2.4259982368377733 AND catalog_page.cp_catalog_page_sk >= 9211.119124129818 GROUP BY date_dim.d_day_name ORDER BY date_dim.d_day_name;

SELECT SUM(web_sales.ws_bill_hdemo_sk + web_sales.ws_bill_customer_sk) as agg_0 FROM web_sales JOIN customer ON web_sales.ws_ship_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk JOIN customer_address ON customer.c_current_addr_sk = customer_address.ca_address_sk JOIN household_demographics ON customer.c_current_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk JOIN date_dim ON customer.c_first_sales_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN customer_demographics ON web_sales.ws_ship_cdemo_sk = customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk JOIN web_site ON web_sales.ws_web_site_sk = web_site.web_site_sk JOIN web_returns ON customer_address.ca_address_sk = web_returns.wr_refunded_addr_sk  WHERE customer_demographics.cd_gender IN ('M') AND web_site.web_country LIKE '%Stat%es%' AND customer.c_birth_month <= 7.358174451376648 AND (customer_address.ca_state IN ('KY', 'AK', 'OR', 'ME', 'NM', 'DE', 'PA') OR (customer_address.ca_state IN ('IA', 'KS') AND customer_address.ca_state IN ('DE', 'MD', 'ME', 'MO'))) AND date_dim.d_date_sk >= 2431009.906023758 AND (web_sales.ws_wholesale_cost <= 16.735184603776915 OR web_sales.ws_web_site_sk >= 4.8873894056148455 OR web_sales.ws_wholesale_cost <= 92.65214364269922) HAVING SUM(web_sales.ws_bill_hdemo_sk + web_sales.ws_bill_customer_sk) != 253575.37166430717;

SELECT customer_demographics.cd_marital_status, customer_demographics.cd_education_status, MAX(catalog_sales.cs_item_sk + web_sales.ws_coupon_amt) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM customer_demographics JOIN store_returns ON customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk = store_returns.sr_cdemo_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk = catalog_sales.cs_bill_cdemo_sk JOIN web_sales ON customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk = web_sales.ws_ship_cdemo_sk  WHERE customer_demographics.cd_dep_college_count >= 3.8672019051264406 AND customer_demographics.cd_credit_rating = 'Low Risk' AND catalog_sales.cs_ship_cdemo_sk <= 1014834.5622645546 AND (catalog_sales.cs_call_center_sk <= 11.79439378218879 OR (catalog_sales.cs_call_center_sk >= 23.348342801956964 AND catalog_sales.cs_call_center_sk <= 13.578335671555102)) AND store_returns.sr_cdemo_sk >= 906186.7968591012 AND customer_demographics.cd_marital_status IN ('U', 'W', 'M') GROUP BY customer_demographics.cd_marital_status, customer_demographics.cd_education_status ORDER BY customer_demographics.cd_marital_status, customer_demographics.cd_education_status;

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, AVG(inventory.inv_quantity_on_hand + inventory.inv_warehouse_sk) as agg_1 FROM inventory  WHERE inventory.inv_date_sk <= 2451929.4028568235 AND inventory.inv_warehouse_sk <= 5.027919702283409 AND inventory.inv_quantity_on_hand <= 608.2160049677589 AND (inventory.inv_item_sk >= 64912.32796012113 OR inventory.inv_item_sk >= 66547.49419533074);

SELECT store.s_rec_start_date, date_dim.d_following_holiday, promotion.p_channel_dmail, SUM(web_returns.wr_return_amt) as agg_0, MAX(promotion.p_item_sk + web_sales.ws_sold_time_sk) as agg_1 FROM catalog_sales JOIN call_center ON catalog_sales.cs_call_center_sk = call_center.cc_call_center_sk JOIN item ON catalog_sales.cs_item_sk = item.i_item_sk JOIN catalog_returns ON item.i_item_sk = catalog_returns.cr_item_sk JOIN household_demographics ON catalog_returns.cr_returning_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk JOIN customer_demographics ON catalog_returns.cr_returning_cdemo_sk = customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk JOIN web_returns ON customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk = web_returns.wr_returning_cdemo_sk JOIN promotion ON catalog_sales.cs_promo_sk = promotion.p_promo_sk JOIN date_dim ON catalog_sales.cs_ship_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN store ON date_dim.d_date_sk = store.s_closed_date_sk JOIN web_sales ON date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk  WHERE date_dim.d_current_quarter = 'Y' AND household_demographics.hd_buy_potential NOT LIKE '%1001%-5000%' AND promotion.p_promo_name IN ('pri', 'cally', 'ation') AND date_dim.d_current_month IN ('Y', 'N') AND call_center.cc_city NOT LIKE '%Mi%dway%' AND date_dim.d_day_name LIKE '%Saturd%ay%' AND item.i_class != 'fishing' AND item.i_container LIKE '%Unknown%' AND catalog_sales.cs_ship_cdemo_sk >= 1148291.7100940207 AND item.i_category_id >= 3.4753595069843755 GROUP BY store.s_rec_start_date, date_dim.d_following_holiday, promotion.p_channel_dmail HAVING SUM(web_returns.wr_return_amt) != 1298.9991210783626 ORDER BY store.s_rec_start_date, date_dim.d_following_holiday, promotion.p_channel_dmail LIMIT 1000;

SELECT date_dim.d_holiday, time_dim.t_sub_shift, date_dim.d_following_holiday, SUM(date_dim.d_qoy + store_returns.sr_fee) as agg_0 FROM customer_address JOIN store_returns ON customer_address.ca_address_sk = store_returns.sr_addr_sk JOIN customer ON store_returns.sr_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk JOIN store_sales ON customer_address.ca_address_sk = store_sales.ss_addr_sk JOIN household_demographics ON store_returns.sr_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk JOIN time_dim ON store_returns.sr_return_time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk JOIN web_returns ON customer.c_customer_sk = web_returns.wr_refunded_customer_sk JOIN date_dim ON customer.c_first_shipto_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk  WHERE (date_dim.d_current_year IN ('Y') OR date_dim.d_current_year = 'Y') AND (household_demographics.hd_buy_potential IN ('501-1000', '5001-10000') OR household_demographics.hd_buy_potential LIKE '%1001-500%0%' OR household_demographics.hd_buy_potential NOT LIKE '%5%001-10000%') AND customer_address.ca_city IN ('Lakeview') AND web_returns.wr_web_page_sk >= 25.505336812515154 AND date_dim.d_holiday IN ('N', 'Y') AND customer.c_customer_sk <= 158001.4961252004 GROUP BY date_dim.d_holiday, time_dim.t_sub_shift, date_dim.d_following_holiday HAVING SUM(date_dim.d_qoy + store_returns.sr_fee) >= 52.76364266520005 ORDER BY date_dim.d_holiday, time_dim.t_sub_shift, date_dim.d_following_holiday LIMIT 10;

SELECT call_center.cc_market_manager, date_dim.d_current_year, call_center.cc_name, SUM(web_sales.ws_bill_customer_sk) as agg_0 FROM call_center JOIN date_dim ON call_center.cc_open_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN web_page ON date_dim.d_date_sk = web_page.wp_creation_date_sk JOIN web_sales ON web_page.wp_web_page_sk = web_sales.ws_web_page_sk JOIN catalog_returns ON date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_returns.cr_returned_date_sk JOIN warehouse ON web_sales.ws_warehouse_sk = warehouse.w_warehouse_sk JOIN customer ON web_sales.ws_ship_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk JOIN household_demographics ON customer.c_current_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk JOIN store_returns ON date_dim.d_date_sk = store_returns.sr_returned_date_sk JOIN customer_address ON web_sales.ws_bill_addr_sk = customer_address.ca_address_sk  WHERE customer_address.ca_country != 'United States' AND customer_address.ca_suite_number LIKE '%270%' AND warehouse.w_street_name IN ('Elm Madison', '6th ', 'View First') GROUP BY call_center.cc_market_manager, date_dim.d_current_year, call_center.cc_name ORDER BY call_center.cc_market_manager, date_dim.d_current_year, call_center.cc_name;

SELECT date_dim.d_following_holiday, store.s_market_desc, time_dim.t_am_pm, AVG(store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk + catalog_sales.cs_ext_ship_cost) as agg_0, MAX(store_sales.ss_net_paid + catalog_sales.cs_ship_hdemo_sk) as agg_1 FROM promotion JOIN store_sales ON promotion.p_promo_sk = store_sales.ss_promo_sk JOIN date_dim ON store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN catalog_page ON date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_page.cp_end_date_sk JOIN web_page ON date_dim.d_date_sk = web_page.wp_access_date_sk JOIN customer_demographics ON store_sales.ss_cdemo_sk = customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON promotion.p_promo_sk = catalog_sales.cs_promo_sk JOIN store ON date_dim.d_date_sk = store.s_closed_date_sk JOIN web_sales ON date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_ship_date_sk JOIN time_dim ON web_sales.ws_sold_time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk JOIN ship_mode ON web_sales.ws_ship_mode_sk = ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk  WHERE promotion.p_channel_radio != 'N' AND store.s_rec_end_date NOT LIKE '%1999-03%-13%' AND (catalog_page.cp_catalog_page_number >= 55.79051565125775 OR (catalog_page.cp_description NOT LIKE '%poli%ce%' AND catalog_page.cp_catalog_page_number >= 38.09092827669551)) AND customer_demographics.cd_gender != 'M' AND (ship_mode.sm_code != 'SEA' OR ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk >= 9.184592159675448) AND (customer_demographics.cd_education_status NOT LIKE '%Unkn%own%' OR customer_demographics.cd_marital_status != 'U') AND web_page.wp_type != 'protected' AND customer_demographics.cd_credit_rating LIKE '%Low%' AND customer_demographics.cd_dep_employed_count >= 1.0742895746430303 AND time_dim.t_time >= 85005.338604708 AND store_sales.ss_cdemo_sk <= 274313.66474061244 AND ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_id != 'AAAAAAAAJAAAAAAA' GROUP BY date_dim.d_following_holiday, store.s_market_desc, time_dim.t_am_pm HAVING MAX(store_sales.ss_net_paid + catalog_sales.cs_ship_hdemo_sk) != 5322.7883065847545 ORDER BY date_dim.d_following_holiday, store.s_market_desc, time_dim.t_am_pm;

SELECT customer.c_last_name, SUM(customer.c_last_review_date_sk + web_returns.wr_refunded_addr_sk) as agg_0, AVG(catalog_sales.cs_warehouse_sk) as agg_1 FROM income_band JOIN household_demographics ON income_band.ib_income_band_sk = household_demographics.hd_income_band_sk JOIN web_returns ON household_demographics.hd_demo_sk = web_returns.wr_returning_hdemo_sk JOIN catalog_returns ON household_demographics.hd_demo_sk = catalog_returns.cr_refunded_hdemo_sk JOIN web_page ON web_returns.wr_web_page_sk = web_page.wp_web_page_sk JOIN item ON web_returns.wr_item_sk = item.i_item_sk JOIN customer ON web_returns.wr_refunded_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk JOIN ship_mode ON catalog_returns.cr_ship_mode_sk = ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON customer.c_customer_sk = catalog_sales.cs_ship_customer_sk JOIN customer_demographics ON catalog_returns.cr_returning_cdemo_sk = customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk  WHERE item.i_manager_id >= 84.22530973509156 AND web_page.wp_web_page_id != 'AAAAAAAAIFAAAAAA' AND catalog_returns.cr_returning_hdemo_sk >= 3867.526867577201 AND item.i_rec_start_date NOT LIKE '%19%97-10-27%' AND customer.c_current_addr_sk <= 79867.10251008986 AND customer_demographics.cd_dep_employed_count <= 0.7751177153945101 AND customer.c_first_name IN ('Anisha', 'Altagracia', 'Genevieve', 'Dick') AND customer_demographics.cd_credit_rating LIKE '%Goo%d%' AND ship_mode.sm_type != 'EXPRESS' AND ship_mode.sm_type LIKE '%REGULA%R%' AND customer_demographics.cd_marital_status IN ('S', 'M') GROUP BY customer.c_last_name ORDER BY customer.c_last_name;

SELECT MIN(catalog_sales.cs_item_sk) as agg_0, MIN(catalog_sales.cs_bill_addr_sk) as agg_1, MAX(catalog_returns.cr_refunded_hdemo_sk + catalog_returns.cr_return_quantity) as agg_2 FROM web_returns JOIN customer ON web_returns.wr_refunded_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk JOIN catalog_returns ON customer.c_customer_sk = catalog_returns.cr_refunded_customer_sk JOIN store_returns ON customer.c_customer_sk = store_returns.sr_customer_sk JOIN customer_address ON customer.c_current_addr_sk = customer_address.ca_address_sk JOIN date_dim ON store_returns.sr_returned_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON customer_address.ca_address_sk = catalog_sales.cs_ship_addr_sk  WHERE date_dim.d_first_dom <= 2445764.806981731 AND customer_address.ca_city LIKE '%Mount%' AND store_returns.sr_ticket_number <= 136105.00746459534 AND customer_address.ca_location_type != 'apartment' AND catalog_sales.cs_ship_hdemo_sk <= 1041.8172186970571 AND catalog_sales.cs_coupon_amt >= 0.0;

SELECT item.i_color, item.i_category, AVG(item.i_manufact_id) as agg_0, MIN(store_sales.ss_net_profit + store_returns.sr_fee) as agg_1 FROM customer_demographics JOIN store_sales ON customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk = store_sales.ss_cdemo_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk = catalog_sales.cs_ship_cdemo_sk JOIN store_returns ON customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk = store_returns.sr_cdemo_sk JOIN item ON store_returns.sr_item_sk = item.i_item_sk JOIN customer ON catalog_sales.cs_ship_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk JOIN customer_address ON catalog_sales.cs_bill_addr_sk = customer_address.ca_address_sk JOIN web_sales ON customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk = web_sales.ws_ship_cdemo_sk  WHERE customer.c_salutation LIKE '%M%iss%' AND customer.c_first_sales_date_sk <= 2451965.3338537905 AND store_returns.sr_fee <= 16.3377307104251 AND customer_address.ca_gmt_offset >= -6.0 AND customer.c_current_addr_sk <= 64334.119798541666 AND web_sales.ws_ship_hdemo_sk <= 4133.415060315986 AND customer_demographics.cd_dep_employed_count <= 2.0 AND store_returns.sr_reversed_charge >= 178.00768757408048 AND web_sales.ws_bill_addr_sk <= 149548.1117505559 AND web_sales.ws_bill_hdemo_sk >= 5798.150731619061 AND item.i_units LIKE '%P%allet%' AND customer.c_birth_year >= 1928.6188591598648 AND store_sales.ss_sold_time_sk >= 57716.394723041834 AND (store_sales.ss_ticket_number <= 1701164.3428297648 OR store_sales.ss_ext_list_price >= 1651.0636190521038) GROUP BY item.i_color, item.i_category ORDER BY item.i_color, item.i_category;

SELECT date_dim.d_current_month, date_dim.d_current_week, AVG(catalog_returns.cr_call_center_sk) as agg_0, AVG(catalog_returns.cr_returned_time_sk) as agg_1, AVG(promotion.p_cost) as agg_2 FROM item JOIN inventory ON item.i_item_sk = inventory.inv_item_sk JOIN promotion ON item.i_item_sk = promotion.p_item_sk JOIN web_sales ON promotion.p_promo_sk = web_sales.ws_promo_sk JOIN customer_demographics ON web_sales.ws_ship_cdemo_sk = customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk JOIN catalog_returns ON customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk = catalog_returns.cr_refunded_cdemo_sk JOIN customer ON web_sales.ws_bill_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON customer.c_customer_sk = catalog_sales.cs_ship_customer_sk JOIN date_dim ON promotion.p_end_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN catalog_page ON catalog_returns.cr_catalog_page_sk = catalog_page.cp_catalog_page_sk  WHERE web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk >= 2450912.8678058223 AND customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk >= 1771276.6601685311 AND customer.c_preferred_cust_flag IS NULL AND inventory.inv_warehouse_sk >= 5.700125407589639 AND (web_sales.ws_bill_hdemo_sk >= 4585.195447542972 OR web_sales.ws_ext_wholesale_cost >= 3266.7427407665937) GROUP BY date_dim.d_current_month, date_dim.d_current_week ORDER BY date_dim.d_current_month, date_dim.d_current_week;

SELECT MIN(catalog_returns.cr_fee + store_returns.sr_net_loss) as agg_0, SUM(ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk + catalog_returns.cr_return_amt_inc_tax) as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM customer JOIN catalog_returns ON customer.c_customer_sk = catalog_returns.cr_refunded_customer_sk JOIN customer_demographics ON catalog_returns.cr_refunded_cdemo_sk = customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk JOIN time_dim ON catalog_returns.cr_returned_time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk JOIN web_returns ON time_dim.t_time_sk = web_returns.wr_returned_time_sk JOIN ship_mode ON catalog_returns.cr_ship_mode_sk = ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk JOIN store_returns ON customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk = store_returns.sr_cdemo_sk JOIN web_sales ON customer.c_customer_sk = web_sales.ws_bill_customer_sk JOIN store ON store_returns.sr_store_sk = store.s_store_sk JOIN date_dim ON web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN item ON web_sales.ws_item_sk = item.i_item_sk  WHERE (customer_demographics.cd_gender != 'F' OR customer_demographics.cd_education_status NOT LIKE '%Advanced%' OR customer_demographics.cd_gender = 'M') AND time_dim.t_am_pm = 'PM' AND date_dim.d_year >= 2039.124957039407 AND ship_mode.sm_type NOT LIKE '%REGULA%R%' AND customer_demographics.cd_gender != 'F' AND customer.c_first_shipto_date_sk >= 2450329.422659447 AND store.s_market_manager != 'Richard Greene' AND store.s_state LIKE '%SD%' AND ship_mode.sm_code NOT LIKE '%SEA%' AND date_dim.d_current_day != 'N' AND customer_demographics.cd_marital_status IN ('U', 'S', 'D', 'M');

SELECT household_demographics.hd_buy_potential, COUNT(*) as agg_0, MAX(catalog_sales.cs_ship_date_sk) as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM catalog_sales JOIN household_demographics ON catalog_sales.cs_bill_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk  WHERE household_demographics.hd_buy_potential IN ('0-500') AND catalog_sales.cs_net_paid_inc_ship >= 281.2521631035775 AND (household_demographics.hd_demo_sk >= 4705.06656690158 OR household_demographics.hd_demo_sk >= 6211.761084349717) AND household_demographics.hd_income_band_sk <= 3.2712757878374776 AND household_demographics.hd_dep_count >= 1.5091604125010512 AND household_demographics.hd_buy_potential != '>10000' AND (catalog_sales.cs_ext_sales_price <= 270.2532994281288 OR (catalog_sales.cs_ext_sales_price >= 388.70245516877225 AND catalog_sales.cs_ext_sales_price <= 61.54176344372403)) AND catalog_sales.cs_ship_date_sk <= 2450913.3773107985 AND (catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk <= 2450944.014521916 OR catalog_sales.cs_bill_addr_sk <= 16581.17147732603) AND catalog_sales.cs_quantity <= 97.24265590117294 AND catalog_sales.cs_bill_hdemo_sk >= 3835.200902558275 AND (catalog_sales.cs_bill_customer_sk <= 116935.10719240342 OR (catalog_sales.cs_warehouse_sk <= 8.135220574720574 AND catalog_sales.cs_bill_customer_sk <= 292833.0148250785)) AND catalog_sales.cs_net_profit >= 1830.46257875341 GROUP BY household_demographics.hd_buy_potential HAVING COUNT(*) <= 0 ORDER BY household_demographics.hd_buy_potential;
